nodes.text: HoloNet News Report: Wookiee Revolt Quelled on Kashyyyk
HoloNet News Report: Wookiee Revolt Quelled on Kashyyyk is the second video from the Star Wars Rebels tie-in website, Holonetnews.com. It was posted on July 23, 2014.

In HoloNet News's top story of the day, the Imperial broadcaster Alton Kastle reported that the 212th Attack Battalion led by General Kahdah had quelled a Wookiee revolt on the Wookiee home planet of Kashyyyk. Under the pretext of safeguarding Imperial citizens, civilian travel to the planet was restricted with access only being granted for official government business.
